{"tid":307772,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實泛民同示威者割席最多只能算係私怨","createTime":"2017-07-03T15:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T20:27:16.000Z","uid":64806,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ab076380db0e6e358ffad0b9f2fa16179db178","tid":307772,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"但係班本土派就成日提呢件事<br />\n用議席去打擊泛民主派<br />\n減弱泛民主派抗共實力<br />\n然後仲要扮到理直氣壯<br />\n知唔知醜？<br />\n<br />\n魚蛋下場係點？<br />\n如果泛民唔堅守和理非抗爭<br />\n搞到好多人「勇武」<br />\n只會令更多人前途盡喪<br />\n<br />\n抗爭時好多人會熱血上腦<br />\n冇左理性<br />\n所以大台其實有需要<br />\n希望泛民下次再有大型抗爭<br />\n唔好再以觀眾自發為榮<br />\n因為冇泛民根本冇咁多人出黎<br />\n到時有人打差佬<br />\n輿論都係入你地數<br />\n<br />\n經過魚革後<br />\n和理非抗爭成本都大左<br />\n我唔想以後和理非示威都要比差佬打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a300b08b04f58761af577d027a94ad9bc7857b","tid":307772,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb42cee3d99b0141d58c65d98adf4d9c7b75ef9","tid":307772,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857a6da79833161845d6fcbfa83d8f7c0ce66bdc","tid":307772,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7110baa888085e1de88f44e24874cdfcf8b2040","tid":307772,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73e0ce18b0d41feb48e5a4f71c80c28e044664a","tid":307772,"uid":65649,"like":1,